<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Matches the ID number of the Conte=
nt item</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>Id\ContentType</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Matches the ID number of the Conte=
nt Type that the Content item is an instance of</td>
</tr>
